SampleCoordinateUnit: normalized 2d image space (image width/height). Bounds = x: [0, 1], y: [0, 1]; center = (0.5, 0.5)
ScreenSize: insert screen size in m, excluding screen borders
ScreenRefreshRate: refresh rate of screen in Hz; 60 fps?
Manufacturer: Manufacturer of the equipment that produced the measurements
DeviceSerialNumber: The serial number of the equipment that produced the measurements. can use pseudonym
AverageCalibrationError: Average calibration error in visual degree; i don't think we have that
EyeCameraSettings: any settings that influence the resolution and quality of the eye imagery. Autowhitebalance? Changes in sharpness?
